  "description": "This individual is an undead human of gaunt proportions, with pale_green skinTone stretched tightly over sharp cheekbones and a long jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets and remain fixed in an unblinking, cavern-hardened stare. Gray hair, kept in a shortknot, exposes a scalp marked by old fissure-like lines and uneven texture typical of long desiccation. The body bears an enduring rigidity and brittle carriage that defines those bound to the echoing dark rather than the living world.",
